name: MongoDB-prefPane
tagline: MongoDB Preference Pane for Mac OS X
body:
![Screenshot](http://tessus.github.io/MongoDB-prefPane/MongoDB-prefPane.png)

### Prerequisites

Does not include MongoDB binaries, therefore you first need to install them from http://www.mongodb.org/downloads

### Installation

* Download the [binary](https://github.com/tessus/MongoDB-prefPane/releases/latest) of the latest release
* Extract it
* Double-click the MongoDB.prefPane file

### Problems, Bugs, Ideas, Praise

Please open a ticket [here](https://github.com/tessus/MongoDB-prefPane/issues).
